{"tid":441463,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺一句\"我份人係咁架啦\"大撚晒","createTime":"2017-10-19T16:14:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-21T10:46:59.000Z","uid":142894,"like":124,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d9180790f380cfaf5de1b290cc612a251a6551b0","tid":441463,"uid":142894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T16:14:01.000Z","msg":"即係叫你做野爽手d，唔好咁慢，你就答一句我份人係咁架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n叫人唔好咁口臭咁mean成日串人，你又答我份人係咁架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n叫你比d禮貌，體諒下人，對人nice d 唔好成日針鋒相對，你又答我份人係咁架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n乜撚野叫我份人係咁架啦，屋企未撚教過你處世做人呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都明個個人都有唔同嘅性格，但係待人接物呢啲嘢係咪應該個個都要學好呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你老味下下搵呢句嘢出嚟做擋箭牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲星座撚仲撚煩，成日話我個星座係小氣啲架啦，做乜鳩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 認為應該屌撚柒呢啲人嘅<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我份人係咁架啦"},{"pid":"ff7f074c820dba5e31f288ffce5ae38e679cb006","tid":441463,"uid":142894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T03:37:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0947ae7215802a008f20de200d439a09e4c24d2","tid":441463,"uid":5190,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T03:39:30.000Z","msg":"投投投 你煩唔煩呀"},{"pid":"8d60ded3d9a86c0ef2c27a5b65584ab2245660cd","tid":441463,"uid":76913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T03:41:20.000Z","msg":"你份人係咪咁架？"},{"pid":"15460648dd1988926e9e8f395910ba5d055f7f85","tid":441463,"uid":17958,"like":0,"